history.content:
Want to hear the answers to the biggest questions in Quantum Computing? Here is your chance in the panel, Horizons in Quantum Computing, hosted by Quantum Computing at Berkeley (QCB). We will have four experts from industry and academia. We invited:

- Denise Ruffner (VP of Business Development at IonQ)
- Fabio Sanches (QC Ware Product Manager)
- Eleanor Rieffel (NASA Senior Research Scientist Lead)
- Simone Severini (Director of Quantum Computing at AWS).

Mark your calendars! On February 10th, at 6pm, you will be able to learn about the current state of the field, ask your burning questions, and mingle with distinguished professionals and researchers during our Zoom mixer. RSVP now at https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScIISuAYZZRrTgC7q43HadSpT6B48cGlnT7tqDRZmoqoS1TQw/viewform


Welcome to our Slack channel too at https://join.slack.com/t/qcberkeley/shared_invite/zt-4fjgc7kh-TEmwUZJzQlOdt8CDsfKaFg
